" Mac Specify================
"map Ctrl + E in normal mode to copy to clipboard
nnoremap <C-E> "*yy
"map Ctrl + E in visual mode to copy to clipboard
vnoremap <C-W> "*y
"past clipboard in normal mode, if in visual using CMD+v
nnoremap <C-D> o<Esc>"*p

set clipboard=unnamed     "set copy to system clipboard

" Linux General===============
" Finding Files
"set path+=**
"set wildmenu

"set cindent
"filetype plugin indent on
" show existing tab with 4 spaces width
set tabstop=4
" when indenting with '>', use 4 spaces width
